headline: Daleep Singh, former U.S. deputy national security advisor, rejoins PGIM Fixed Income
summary: NEWARK, N.J., March 17, 2025--PGIM Fixed Income, one of the largest fixed income managers globally with $837 billion in assets under management, welcomes Daleep Singh back as vice chair, chief global economist and head of global macroeconomic research, effective April 21, 2025.
